sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Mgr as PPC Manager
    participant AI as AI Analyst
    participant Data as Account Data

    Mgr->>AI: This account is performing poorly
    AI-->>Mgr: Sharpen it — which metric,<br/>before vs now, over what period?
    Mgr->>AI: CPA rose from $38 to $59 in January

    AI->>AI: List 5-8 hypotheses BEFORE touching data
    Note over AI,Data: Internal changes, external factors,<br/>measurement issues — all three<br/>categories, every time.

    loop One evidence layer at a time
        AI->>Data: Pull one layer —<br/>performance, traffic,<br/>segments, change history
        Data-->>AI: Findings
        AI->>AI: Update each hypothesis —<br/>supported, weakened, eliminated
    end

    AI-->>Mgr: Verdict — one root cause,<br/>the evidence that proves it, one specific fix
    Note over Mgr,AI: Every hypothesis ends confirmed or<br/>eliminated — never quietly forgotten.<br/>Inconclusive is a valid answer. Guessing is not.
